**Open Anaconda prompt**

**Only on first run:**
conda env create -f environment.yml --name QAFKA_env
conda install -c anaconda ipykernel

**Every time you want to open the notebook:**
python -m ipykernel install --user --name=QAFKA_env
jupyter notebook

**The jupyter notebook window will open in your browser, then locate the QAFKA directory and open the file called main.ipynb**


